from\": 990, \"to\": 1003}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Claire Michel, a member of the relay, is unfortunately ill and has to withdraw from the competition.\\\"\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1108, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1007, \"end\": 1020, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Claire_Michel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Claire Michel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Claire_Michel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Claire_Michel\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a member\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1030}, {\"ngram\": \"the relay\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1106}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Belgian media reported that Michel has contracted E. coli.\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1168, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1110, \"end\": 1117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 0.9999844488858823, \"rank\": 9.785719495279528e-06, \"text\": \"Belgian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Michel\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1144}, {\"ngram\": \"E. coli\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1167}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The team statement did not confirm that, but notably added: \\\"The COIB and Belgian Triathlon hope that lessons will be learned for the next triathlon competitions at the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1353, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1244, \"end\": 1251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 0.9999844488858823, \"rank\": 9.785719495279528e-06, \"text\": \"Belgian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}, {\"begin\": 1252, \"end\": 1261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Triathlon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.936307976749559e-17, \"text\": \"Triathlon\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Triathlon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Triathlon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The team statement\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1188}, {\"ngram\": \"The COIB\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1239}, {\"ngram\": \"lessons\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1279}, {\"ngram\": \"the next triathlon competitions\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1331}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1352}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are thinking here of the guarantee of training days, competition days and the format of the competitions which must be clarified in advance and ensure that there is no uncertainty for the athletes, the entourage and the supporters.\\\"\", \"from\": 1355, \"to\": 1591, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the guarantee\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1393}, {\"ngram\": \"training days\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1410}, {\"ngram\": \"the competitions\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1463}, {\"ngram\": \"advance\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1498}, {\"ngram\": \"no uncertainty\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1538}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1555}, {\"ngram\": \"the entourage\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1570}, {\"ngram\": \"the supporters\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1589}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Switzerland have made a change to their line-up after Adrien Briffod also fell ill, with Simon Westermann taking his place.\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1727, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1604, \"end\": 1615, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"score\": 0.9999819582519196, \"rank\": 1.5186846020012518e-05, \"text\": \"Switzerland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\"}, {\"begin\": 1658, \"end\": 1664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Adrien\", \"score\": 0.9999999913347892, \"rank\": 4.224829325229484e-09